title: The Jboy Show - Lane Kiffin's LSU Audition
itunes:title: The Jboy Show - Lane Kiffin's LSU Audition
description:
Hours before an exciting week 8, Jake tells you why the LSU game might mean a little bit more to Lane Kiffin, why the Tennessee-Alabama rivalry is dead, and Blain finally pays up his hot wings bet. Make sure to check us out LIVE on Youtube every day at 3pm EST, plus follow us @thejboyshow on all social media platforms.
